name: ground-water-contamination-susceptibility-in-minnesota
notes: A broad, generalized interpretation of ground water contamination susceptibility for the state, based on modeling relying on data inputs from the MLMIS40 (40-acre raster) soils and geology data, with additional geology inputs. This layer is not appropriate for site-specific use.
